| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1806 — Recovery Inhibition (noescape)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 68aa0675-f0c3-57cf-bd1b-2f756510a6b7"
